data.description: Super cute  bungalow located in Kannapolis! Home features 3 bedrooms with 1.5 bathrooms and just over 1,400 square feet. Gorgeous vinyl planking floors throughout, with faux wood blinds in all windows. The kitchen features granite counter tops and stainless appliances. The large back deck overlooks your expansive backyard. Spacious den area could also be used for a dining room or both. Office/playroom could be used for a 4th bedroom, however, it does not have a closet.
